snippet.title: WWE 2K25 - The Island Reveal Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
For the first time in WWE 2K franchise history, step outside the ropes and onto The Island. In this immersive WWE-themed world, complete quests, take on challenges, compete in live events, and upgrade and customize your MySUPERSTAR through multiple storyline chapters.
